data.meta_description: 121 likes, 2 comments - charliebirdparkerofficial on May 31, 2024: "64 days #KansasCity it’s “Spotlight Charlie Parker” ➡️ Kansas City’s jazz presenters, art exhibitors, and civic and cultural organizations come together to host jam sessions, tours, lectures, exhibits, panel discussions, workshops, and concerts celebrating Kansas City’s own, Charlie Parker! Visit http://spotlightcharlieparker.org (link in bio and stories too) to learn more @kansascityjazzalive @thefollytheater @kansascityjazzorchestra + more".
